These beaded clips can be made with a name or without. all beads are wooden and non toxic and come in a variety of shapes and colours. The thread is 100% cotton and the letter cubes can also be in different colours. 
Please see my blog for examples of past clips.
I just need to know the name you wish, colours you prefer and I will make it up for you.
The clip is lead free nickel and is covered with a playful wodden shape to look extra cute and keep fingers away from the clip. It has no sharp edges so wont ruin clothes. 
If you have any questions please ask. :)
My blog: http://vanessasdummyclips.blogspot.com/

They come in many colours and designs so take a look here for my ribbon designs:

Ribbon clips come with a press stud on the end for easy attachment to dummies with a handle. The other end connects to their clothes or the pram with a lead free metal clip. It has plastic teeth on the inside of the clip so it won't tear or damage clothing but it will grip and take hold. The smooth edges ensure it won't catch on anything.
For use with a round or smooth dummy just attach a Mam clip with the press stud end. MAM clips are sold in the accessories category.

$1.20 postage for up to 2 clips.

Please see here for my ribbon selection. http://s353.photobucket.com/albums/r375/alisia1981/Ribbons-%20all%20available%20colours/?start=all
